# IMPORTANT: without this file, `COPY . .` in the Dockerfile silently
# overlays the VPS host's node_modules/ on top of the fresh `npm ci`
# install, producing a Frankenstein dependency tree at runtime. We
# discovered this on 2026-05-01 when a stale lru-cache@5.1.1 left over
# on the box from April clobbered the locked v11.3.5 and crash-looped
# the backend with `lru_cache_1.LRUCache is not a constructor`.
# Keep this list pruned — anything that lives in the working tree but
# isn't part of the source-of-truth deployable should be excluded here.

# Build artifacts (regenerated inside the image)
node_modules
dist
build

# Local environment / secrets — must never end up in the image
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / OS noise
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.log
*.swp

# Test / coverage output
coverage
.nyc_output
junit*.xml

# Git metadata
.git
.gitignore

# Docker meta (no need to ship into the image)
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# Misc dev tooling
*.tsbuildinfo
